# Drug Classification with Deep Learning

This project uses a neural network (Keras & TensorFlow) to classify drug types based on patient features.

## Dataset
The dataset contains patient information (e.g., age, blood pressure, cholesterol, etc.) with drug type labels.

## Model
- Input: 5 features
- Hidden layers: Dense + Dropout
- Output: 5 classes (softmax)
- Loss: categorical_crossentropy

## Results
- Accuracy: ~80% on test set

Confusion matrix:

![confusion_matrix](images/confusion_matrix.png)

## How to run
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python src/train.py
